longBusinessSummary: Mazaya Real Estate Development Q.P.S.C. engages in the building, buying, selling, and operating residential and commercial real estate projects. It is involved in the establishment and management of residential compounds and projects for rental purposes; purchase of land and its development for resale; construction, project feasibility study, and project management; real estate marketing and property management; and maintenance and brokerage activities. The company was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Doha, Qatar.
